# Settlement System
#
# Cross-module linking and packaging for Simple executables.
# Resolves symbols across modules, manages dependencies,
# and produces final SSMF (Simple Static Module Format) files.
#
# Components:
#   linker.spl     - Cross-module symbol resolution
#   container.spl  - Multi-module container lifecycle
#   builder.spl    - SSMF file and executable stub generation
